WEBVTT

00:08:29.019 --> 00:08:30.899
and again it doesn't have to be you,

00:08:30.899 --> 00:08:33.002
because you can get creative,

00:08:33.002 --> 00:08:36.551
because there is a whole universe 
out there of nominees

00:08:36.551 --> 00:08:38.398
to choose from.

00:08:38.398 --> 00:08:40.734
And nominees are the people that you

00:08:40.734 --> 00:08:45.570
can legally pay to be your company's owner.

00:08:45.570 --> 00:08:47.412
And if you don't want to involve anyone else,

00:08:47.412 --> 00:08:50.275
it doesn't even have to be an actual human being.

00:08:50.275 --> 00:08:53.363
It could be another company.

00:08:53.363 --> 00:08:54.793
And then finally,

00:08:54.793 --> 00:08:56.522
give your company a name

00:08:56.522 --> 00:08:59.253
add a few more details and make your payment.

00:08:59.253 --> 00:09:00.673
And then the service provider